thorwin.math.geo

Class Euler

  • java.lang.Object
    • thorwin.math.geo.Euler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public final class Euler
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Rotation around three axis. Heading (y-axis) applied first, attitude (z-axis) applied second, bank (x-axis) applied last.

    Angle positive direction is determined using the right-hand-rule.

    See Also:
